Once a new player understands Magic's basic rules, the Deck Builder's Toolkit jumpstarts their collection and introduces them to deckbuilding.

Contents:

• 4 fifteen-card booster packs from recent Magic sets
• 100 basic land cards
• 1 deck builder's guide
• 1 Magic quick reference booklet
• 1 reusable card storage box

The Spellslinger Starter Kit lets new players to jump right in to their first game of Magic. It comes with two Standard-legal 60-card decks—designed to create an interactive learning experience for two.
Contents:
• 2 60-card, Standard-legal decks
• 2 Quick-start guides
• Rules and world-of-Magic booklet
• 2 “do no shuffle”/"on your turn" cards
• Two Spindown life counters
